summary: This document contains multiple passenger manifests for flights operated by JEGE, LLC. Each manifest lists details such as departure and arrival times, passenger names, fuel purchased, and flight levels. The manifests are part of the evidence related to the Epstein case, showing the travel patterns and individuals associated with the flights.
